{"word":"διανέμω","slug":"διανέμω","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>διανέμω</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-νεμῶ</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>-νενέμηκα</el>) </el><p/><i>to distribute, apportion</i>, <el>τί τινι</el> <b><a href='S:Aristophanes'>Ar.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>:—<a href='S:Medium, Middle'>Mid.</a> <i>to divide among themselves</i>, <b><a href='S:Plato'>Plat.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Aristotle'>Arist.</a></b>:—<a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>Pass.</a></a>, aor1 <a href='S:infinitive'>inf.</a> <el>διανεμηθῆναι</el> <i>to be spread abroad</i>, <b><a href='S:New Testament'>NTest.</a></b><p/>"}]}